video.title: DC Super Hero Girls
video.synopsis: As Metropolis High students, super teens Wonder Woman, Supergirl, Bumblebee, Batgirl, Zatanna, and Green Lantern fight crime, classwork and crushes.

episodes.synopsis: As Batgirl adjusts to a new school, she meets five other ordinary girls with superpowers, who agree to join forces against Metropolis' villains.
episodes.title: #SweetJustice: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Wonder Woman trains Supergirl, Bumblebee, Batgirl, Zatanna and Green Lantern to become life-saving superheroes as they teach her to be an everyday teen.
episodes.title: #SweetJustice: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: When LexCorp robots threaten to demolish Sweet Justice, the girls fight to save the shop. A disobedient superteen receives an unexpected punishment.
episodes.title: #SweetJustice: Part 3

episodes.synopsis: The super squad schemes to stop Diana from returning home. In Metropolis, a war breaks out between LexCorp robots and the band of newly minted heroes.
episodes.title: #SweetJustice: Part 4

episodes.synopsis: After Zatanna puts her in charge, Supergirl gets a lesson in responsibility thanks to a pair of shapeshifting rabbits that wreak havoc on Metropolis.
episodes.title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting

episodes.synopsis: When supervillain Star Sapphire goes love crazy at homecoming, Green Lantern's nonviolent tactics to fighting are put to the test.
episodes.title: #HateTriangle

episodes.synopsis: Batgirl juggles crime-fighting and burrito-serving obligations when a bank robbery occurs while she’s at work.
episodes.title: #BurritoBucket

episodes.synopsis: When Wonder Woman earns a coveted position on the gymnastics team, a jealous classmate casts an ancient spell that causes a personality change.
episodes.title: #MeetTheCheetah

episodes.synopsis: A brave Bumblebee and the team assemble to stop a villainous plot laid out by Harley Quinn, Star Sapphire, Catwoman, Livewire, Poison Ivy and Giganta.
episodes.title: #Beeline

episodes.synopsis: Annoyed with Superman stealing the spotlight for their heroic deeds, Supergirl works to outshine the glory-seeking superhuman.
episodes.title: #SuperWho?

episodes.synopsis: After a high school mean girl goes viral for posting cruel vids about classmates, Wonder Woman questions the moral integrity of Metropolis.
episodes.title: #ShockItToMe

episodes.synopsis: Despite being bullied at school, pint-sized Bumblebee steps up to calm the wrath of a giant supervillain who attacks the local mall.
episodes.title: #SheMightBeGiant

episodes.synopsis: When Catwoman slinks into the local science exhibit to steal gems, Supergirl is forced to rely on her brain instead of her brawn.
episodes.title: #FightAtTheMuseum

episodes.synopsis: When Gotham's most beloved protector asks Batgirl for help, she must first find a way to keep the secret from her father, Commissioner Jim Gordon.
episodes.title: #FromBatToWorse

episodes.synopsis: During a jam-packed, productive week for Wonder Woman, a handsome new distraction threatens to throw her off course.
episodes.title: #CrushingIt

episodes.synopsis: Unaware of one another's alter egos, Green Lantern and Poison Ivy work together to save an ancient tree from being cut down.
episodes.title: #MisgivingTree

episodes.synopsis: After her magic show is dismissed as fake, an outraged Zatanna accidentally unleashes mischievous creatures who terrorize the pier.
episodes.title: #IllusionsOfGrandeur

episodes.synopsis: Batgirl and Supergirl settle a bet during a highly competitive dog show, where their magically enhanced pups find themselves saving the day.
episodes.title: #BeastsInShow

episodes.synopsis: Trouble lurks in Gotham City's annual geekfest, where Barbara Gordon and her BFF Harleen Quinzel come face to face with each other's super alter egos.
episodes.title: #GothamCon

episodes.synopsis: During a vandalism investigation, the super squad discovers a world domination-hungry trio of powerful Kryptonians.
episodes.title: #DCSuperHeroBoys Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Super teens Wonder Woman, Supergirl, Bumblebee, Batgirl, Zatanna and Green Lantern face off against their boy rivals, the Super Hero Boys.
episodes.title: #DCSuperHeroBoys Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After the heroes tire of Harleen’s antics, she assumes her alter-ego and vandalizes Metropolis with a new villainous crew.
episodes.title: #Frenemies Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Barbara tries to restore her friendship with Harleen as Harley, Catwoman, Poison Ivy, Star Sapphire, Giganta and Livewire face off with the hero girls.
episodes.title: #Frenemies Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Diana bonds with fellow fencer Tatsu while Supergirl, Bumblebee, Batgirl, Zatanna and Green Lantern track down a soul-snatching samurai.
episodes.title: #SoulSisters Part 1

episodes.synopsis: As the girls interfere with Katana’s mission to punish evildoers, Diana helps her new friend become a true hero.
episodes.title: #SoulSisters Part 2

episodes.synopsis: When Bumblebee freaks out over a blemish, Zee schools her on the beauty of stage makeup.
episodes.title: #Abracadabrapalooza

episodes.synopsis: Jessica works to find a purr-fect home for Dexter, an indignant feline from an animal shelter with his own plans for the future.
episodes.title: #Ragecat

episodes.synopsis: Kara’s good-girl reputation takes a hit when she assumes blame for a new supervillain's bad deeds.
episodes.title: #TheGoodTheBadAndTheBizarre

episodes.synopsis: After a gassy incident at a school assembly, Barbara takes advantage of Flash’s time-traveling powers to prevent humiliation.
episodes.title: #BackInAFlash

episodes.synopsis: When the public is led to believe Supergirl has met her demise after a fight with Livewire, Kara uses the opportunity to switch up her heroic persona.
episodes.title: #PowerSurge

episodes.synopsis: When a school assignment demands that the girls care for an egg or lose their summer break, they fight — literally — to protect their vacation.
episodes.title: #ScrambledEggs

episodes.synopsis: As Oliver Queen competes with his rival, Mortimer Drake, for a coveted role in a play, Green Arrow finds himself clashing against a new supervillain.
episodes.title: #DramaQueen

episodes.synopsis: When Lex Luthor uncovers a book with magical powers, the girls hatch a risky plan that involves enlisting the help of an unexpected ally to retrieve it.
episodes.title: #AllyCat Part 1

episodes.synopsis: After Lex Luthor reveals his sinister plot to destroy the world, Catwoman seizes an opportunity to change the narrative.
episodes.title: #AllyCat Part 2

episodes.synopsis: During an overnight camping trip, Poison Ivy and plant zombies attack a powerless super crew.
episodes.title: #Retreat

episodes.synopsis: When a new friend invites Barbara over for dinner, conflict turns out to be on the menu.
episodes.title: #DinnerForFive

episodes.synopsis: Zee must face her insecurities in order to save her super friends after a dream demon holds them captive in their nightmares.
episodes.title: #LivingTheNightmare

episodes.synopsis: Zee is left without her superpowers when an overzealous admirer sets out to be just like her.
episodes.title: #AllAboutZee

episodes.synopsis: Jessica and Karen chaperone Dick Grayson's Metropolis birthday bash but his tween guests are too much to handle.
episodes.title: #TweenTitans

episodes.synopsis: Attempting to carry out a nice deed, Barbara gets caught up in a high school mob boss' scheme.
episodes.title: #EmperorPenguin

episodes.synopsis: Lois Lane tries to secure an internship at the Daily Planet but her assignment to unmask the Super Hero Girls forces them to get creative.
episodes.title: #BreakingNews
